data.description: This charming 4-bedroom, 2-bathroom home has1620 sqft, and offers the perfect blend of modern comfort and rustic charm. Brand new flooring has been installed throughout the entire home. The primary bedroom boasts an attached full bath for your convenience. Admire the unique log-style siding that lends character to the exterior. Nestled on an expansive 33-acre lot in unincorporated Weld County, the possibilities are endless. Enjoy the breathtaking views, and the freedom to have horses, cattle, and more, thanks to the property's generous acreage. With well water and propane gas, you'll relish the independence this home offers. Plus, there is no HOA or Metro Tax to ensure both freedom and affordability. Complete with a small outbuilding/shed for storage. The property is fully fenced to the property lines. Don't miss out on this incredible opportunity to own your slice of the countryside.
